{
  "stem": "6258.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were-- all the time, the airplanes, the German airplanes, were flying overhead and they were bombing us and we were like sitting ducks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not even sitting ducks-- we were just-- I remember in one ditch, waiting while everybody wanted just to get into the earth.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I look, and on the leaves of grass, there was a little ant walking with something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the ant was walking this way and that way and the other way, and finally went up the grass all around.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I said, how strange.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Here is the end of the world, and what the ant cares is how to get with this little piece of-- of-- I don't know, whatever she had there-- to her place.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And somehow, I remember this so well, looking at this ant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It bring me some-- some, you know, feeling of security that after all, the nature has its own ways.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Maybe indifferent to our problems, but somehow there is an order in nature.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then I wasn't so frightened anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Well, but anyway, by the next air raid, we get lost with my mother-- and my mother was somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I was with my father, and I was, as matter of fact, in my mother long coat, because it was cold and-- so anyway, we went near Lemberg.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then, as soon we arrived there-- and there were masses of refugees from all over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then the Russian came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we did not even know what is going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why the Russian came?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why they came from the east, and went up to the Vistula River, also?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So anyway, there we were.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went to a very historic old town, small town, [NON-ENGLISH] near Lemberg.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
